snippet.title: 12 Hours To Die Playthrough Part One
snippet.description:
This is part one of the 12 Hours To Die Playthrough. The game is free on steam, and you can access it via the link below in your browser if you want to download it. If you have already downloaded steam on your computer, you can type in 12 Hours To Die in the search bar if you want to play the game. Thank you!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1345080/12_Hours_to_Die/
